data.description: Are you searching for a home with gorgeous views from every room?  This beautiful home with amazing views of Millerton Lake is perfect for a primary residence , vacation home or short term rental.  You'll love the bright, open floor plan with lots of natural light.  The generously sized kitchen is open to the great room and boasts an island, granite countertops and stainless appliances.  A large deck off the kitchen is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or evening glass of wine as you take in the beautiful scenery.  Three good sized bedrooms are upstairs including a tranquil master suite.  Home is currently being used as a successful short term rental / Airbnb. This amazing property is being sold fully furnished..all furnishings and appliances are to be included in the purchase price at no value, with no warranty. Don't miss out on this great opportunity! This unique property is waiting for you, make an appointment to see it today!
